    These weapons are registered with the game's ItemManager on load.
    
    WeaponType values: 0=None, 1=Pistol, 2=AssaultRifle, 3=SniperRifle, 4=HeavyWeapon, 5=Grenade
    ItemSlot values: 5=WeaponPistol, 6=Weapon, 7=WeaponAugmentation
    SubCategory: 0=None, 1=Pistol, 2=AssaultRifle, 3=SniperRifle, 4=HeavyWeapon, 5=Grenade
  -->
  
